<h1>SWGOH Tools and Guides</h1>
<p>This website has a collection of useful tools and resources for people playing <a href="https://www.ea.com/games/starwars/galaxy-of-heroes">Star Wars&trade; Galaxy of Heroes</a> (SWGOH).</p>

<div class="rect">
  <img src="images/icon_discord.png" width="40" height="40" />
  <p>Want to get in touch, share your tips, or discuss the game? Join our public <b><a href="https://discord.gg/7ThSZJm">Discord Server</a></b>.</p>
</div>
<br class="clear" />

<div class="square">
  <a href="farming.html"><img src="images/icon_shard_farm.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="farming.html">Shard/Gear Farming Calculator</a></b><br />
  <p>A tool that shows you the best way to farm a toon's shards and gear and gives an estimate of the amount of time it will take to do so.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="ships.html"><img src="images/icon_ships.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="ships.html">Ship Farming Calculator</a></b><br />
  <p>A tool that shows you the best way to farm a ship's shards and gives an estimate of the amount of time it will take to do so.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="avatar.html"><img src="images/icon_avatar.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="avatar.html">Avatar Creator</a></b><br />
  <p>Create your own SWGOH Avatar! Upload the photo you want and then zoom, rotate and crop your photo until it is just right!</p>
</div>


<div class="square">
  <a href="squad_planner.html"><img src="images/icon_tw.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="squad_planner.html">Territory War Squad Builder</a></b><br />
  <p>See which of your guild members have the best version of various squads.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="http://shard.swgoh.life/squads.php"><img src="images/icon_squads.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="http://shard.swgoh.life/squads.php">Squad Recommendations</a></b><br />
  <p>Screenshots showing damage from the raids with various squad compositions.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="http://shard.swgoh.life/recruit.php"><img src="images/icon_recruit.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="http://shard.swgoh.life/recruit.php">Guild Recruitment</a></b><br />
  <p>Find a guild that matches your level. Advertise your guild and recruit new members that match your requirements.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="tb.html"><img src="images/icon_tb.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="tb.html">Territory Battle Tools</a></b><br />
  <p>Quickly check to see if you are ready for Territory Battles and predict how many stars your guild can get.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="http://shard.swgoh.life/index.php"><img src="images/icon_shard.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="http://shard.swgoh.life/index.php">Find Your Squad Arena Shard</a></b><br />
  <p>In the arena, you only play against people in your small game shard/server. This tool helps you find and contact your shardmates from Squad Arena.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="http://shard.swgoh.life/fleet.php"><img src="images/icon_fleet.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="http://shard.swgoh.life/fleet.php">Find Your Fleet Arena Shard</a></b><br />
  <p>In the arena, you only play against people in your small game shard/server. This tool helps you find and contact your shardmates from Fleet Arena.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="http://shard.swgoh.life/shop.php"><img src="images/icon_shipments.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="http://shard.swgoh.life/shop.php">Shipments Price Calculator</a></b><br />
  <p>Thinking of buying something from Shipments? Wondering if it's worth it? This will tell you.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="crystals.html"><img src="images/icon_crystals.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="crystals.html">Crystal Farming Guide</a></b><br />
  <p>Shows you where to get crystals for free and how many you can get per day.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="refresh.html"><img src="images/icon_refresh.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="refresh.html">Refresh / Payout Times</a></b><br />
  <p>See when the various in-game stores refresh their wares and when payout times occur.</p>
</div>


<div class="square">
  <a href="mods.html"><img src="images/icon_mods.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="mods.html">Mod Farming Guide</a></b><br />
  <p>Explains how mods work and shows you the drop rates for the different mod varieties.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="discord.html"><img src="images/icon_discord.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="discord.html">Automatic Discord Game Updates</a></b><br />
  <p>This tutorial will explain how to set it up so that official SWGOH game updates will be automatically posted to a channel of your choice on your Discord server.</p>
</div>

<div class="square">
  <a href="buffs.html"><img src="images/icon_buffs.png" width="200" height="200" /></a><br />
  <b><a href="buffs.html">Buffs and Debuffs explained</a></b><br />
  <p>Explains what all those buffs and debuffs actually do.</p>
</div>


